WEBVTT

00:05:59.027 --> 00:06:00.443
to our shopping behavior.

00:06:01.128 --> 00:06:04.917
Take the extra time
to research and think --

00:06:05.539 --> 00:06:07.553
Do I really need this item?

00:06:08.425 --> 00:06:11.534
No: Do I really want this item? --

00:06:12.884 --> 00:06:14.514
before making a purchase.

00:06:14.978 --> 00:06:18.021
And if every one of us adults in the US

00:06:18.045 --> 00:06:21.630
returned five less items this year,

00:06:21.654 --> 00:06:27.762
we would keep 240 million pounds
of clothes out of the landfill.

00:06:28.443 --> 00:06:30.759
Six percent reduction, just like that.